column5: GF & I left the house around 9 this morning for our first trip to the little lake where I keep a boat stash about 1/2 hour away.The bite was on! We normally just bring home enough for the 2 of us to eat that day,but we are having company from southern Ont this week & thought they might enjoy a fish-fry.We were back home by noon!
Nice stringer!!  Ahh, seen one stringer,seen them all,,,,,,,,,,,,,LOL  Nice going.
Looks  like a great morning and a fine meal to me.
Nice stringer Rick!  Was nice to catch up the other day.  Simon.
The fish of summer!  Always nice to be done before the heat kicks up.  I have that same stringer and it's excellent!
Nice shooting!!!!  Come visit man, im probably not to far off.
